name: I Wish Just Once In My Life

metadata.name: JUSTONCE 1/80
metadata.description:
Inspired by a recent fundraiser for a sick friend, I created 'I Wish Just Once', a collection of 80 NFTs from the 17 photos I originally posted on social media. 
The collection's title was taken from a viral response to these photos. 

All proceeds from the sale of these NFTs will be used to support our friend. 

As a newcomer to NFTs, I invite you to visit my [LinkTree](https://linktr.ee/josselinex) to learn more about my upcoming airdrops and exclusive opportunities!

This NFT represents #1/80

❤️Josseline
